Read Me!

DISCLAIMER: IF YOU DON'T INPAINT, YOUR RESULTS MIGHT SUCK!

TWO VERSIONS (I RECOMMEND USING BOTH):

  • ClitPussy1 v1: Trained on SD 1.5 base model, compatible with all models

    • USE THIS LORA FOR INITIAL TXT2IMG GENS

    • For txt2img & img2img: LoRA weight between 0.2-0.6 for best results

      • v1 is meant to be strong, which lets you mix with other LoRAs (ex. face) much more easily

  • ClitPussy1 v1 Inpainting: Trained on LazyMix+, the best all around checkpoint for highly-detailed pussies

    • USE THIS LORA FOR INPAINTING AND/OR UPSCALING

    • For txt2img & img2img: LoRA weight between 0.5-1 for best results (higher values can affect the skin texture more)

Version 1

  • ClitPussy1 v1

    • SD 1.5 base model (best compatibility across all checkpoint models)

    • 576x576

    • 1 epoch, 100 repeats, 26 images

      bucket 0: resolution (448, 576), count: 400

      bucket 1: resolution (448, 704), count: 600

      bucket 2: resolution (512, 640), count: 200

      bucket 3: resolution (576, 576), count: 1400 (majority of images were cropped to 1:1 aspect ratio)

  • ClitPussy1 v1 Inpainting

    • 512x768 (MUST USE 512x768 2:3 ASPECT RATIO FOR BEST RESULTS!)

    • 6 epochs, 25 repeats, 26 images

  • Read Recommended Settings and Notes for tips on how to get the best results

Recommended Settings

  • ChilloutMix derived models (ex. MajicMix, PerfectWorld, RevAnimated) occasionally struggle with this LoRA for who knows why, be patient and INPAINT

  • Make sure you use 'clitpussy1' in positive, and you can also use trigger word 'open_pussy' in positive or negative to finetune result

  • For txt2img: v1 LoRA weight of <=0.6

    • You can generate the composition in txt2img, then edit further with img2img/inpainting with this LoRA or v1 Inpainting LoRA

    • HiRes Upscale: Denoising <=0.3 (higher than 0.3 can result in double butthole - not what you want). I usually use 0.2

    • Put (fingers:1.5) in negative prompt if you don't wanna deal with stupid fingers

    • For animated models, you may need to raise the weight even more depending on the composition (WARNING: CAREFUL NOT TO GO TOO HIGH, MAY NEGATIVELY IMPACT IMAGE QUALITY), then inpaint for a more perfect result

  • For img2img: v1 LoRA weight of 0.4-0.6

  • Inpainting: use ClitPussy1 v1 Inpainting, LoRA weight of 0.5-1

    • Masked Content = Original

    • Inpaint area: Whole Picture for better integration, Only Masked for just masked area - may want to adjust prompt if using Only Masked

    • Padding medium size (ex. 80-100), denoising around 0.2-0.8 depending on how drastic of a change you want (0.45 is a good number)

  • Best models: Real Hot Mix, LazyMix+

    • Real Hot Mix is a mix I created to include LazyMix with some other photoreal models

    • LazyMix+ utilizes Subreddit v3, where you can add "A photo from the ____ subreddit, ____ quality" to the prompt (ex. pussy, GodPussy, or AsiansGoneWild) for more variation

Notes

  • Tips on getting extremely high-quality results:

    1. Generate large batch in txt2img, set v1 LoRA weight lower for full body pics (somewhere between 0.2-0.6). I use Real Hot Mix for all txt2img gens

      • HIGHLY recommend using ControlNet, I mostly use softedge & openpose for composition, recently started using t2ia color grid as well

    2. Select best pics, crop/edit outside of SD, inpaint as needed (ex. v1 Inpainting LoRA)

    3. Insert edited pic into img2img with same/mostly same prompt, LoRA weight around 0.4-0.6

    4. Denoising between 0.2-0.5, generate

    5. Select best pics, crop/edit outside of SD, inpaint as needed (ex. v1 Inpainting LoRA)

    6. Repeat steps 3-5 as many times as needed

    7. Insert edited pic into img2img with same/mostly same prompt

    8. Denoising between 0.1-0.3, upscale: (1.25x-2x), generate

  • Don't forget to go outside and touch grass

Background

I'm a horny dude and I've seen a lot of pussies. I believe they're all unique, like a face. But different pussies also have very repeatable looks/themes. The plan is to create a set of LoRAs with categories of pussy types using images of the same model. Eventually it will be like a catalog to select which LoRA for the type of pussy you're looking for.
